question: Tī 2011 nî 4 goe̍h hòng-sàng ê chi-kan, goân-tiāu lāi-iông ū siōng-koân ê "No. in series" ê kè-ōe sī sím-mih?
Tī 2011 nî 5 goe̍h chheⁿ káu 6 goe̍h chheⁿ boán chi kan, ū kúi hāng ti̍t-sū hòng-sàng?
Tī ài hō͘ "London ê Olympic Aquatic Stadium" ê chiap-ōe ê āu-chi̍t ê kè-ōe, i ê kok-ka sī siáⁿ-mih?
Tī tē-sì kap tē-gō͘ chi̍p chi kan, ū cheng-chhāi ji̍t-su, hō͘-chòe thêng-chí ê sî-kan-kan-ge?
La̍k chhut, chāi hui-Au-chiu kap hui-Pak-Au-chiu ê kok-ka lāi-bīn ê kè-ōe ê su-bo̍k.
Tī lia̍t chhut ê chong-só͘ lāi-bīn, ū kúi-á cha̍p-hun-chi pháiⁿ-sî chham 4 goe̍h bô-kâng ê goe̍h hun chhut ê?
Nā-miâ "Ho̍k-sin New York Siâ-thih Lō͘" ê tiān-sī-kio̍k sī kah-ì tī kúi-ê goe̍h-ji̍t khui-pò͘? Kah-ì án-choáⁿ tńg-se̍h ê tiān-sī-kio̍k ê khui-pò͘ ji̍t-chí sī kúi-ê goe̍h-ji̍ ji̍t?
Tī chia ê chu-liàu lāi-bīn, "No. in series" kap "No. in season" ê chit-tiâu ū siáⁿ-mih koan-hē?
answer: Ū chi̍t ê ti̍t-chiap koh oân-choân ê chha-chē thien-sò͘ koan-hē. Bē-su tiāⁿ-tiāⁿ "No. in season" cheng-ka 1 ê sî, "No. in series" mā tiāⁿ-tiāⁿ cheng-ka 1. Che sī chí tûi-chí liân-sòa--ê chi̍t ê hē-lia̍t ê tiám-siám tī sòaⁿ chìn-tiâu.

question: Tī chit ê su-liāu tiong, ū sím-ê muî-chi̍t hāng lóng ū kāng-ê kè-ta̍t, chiàⁿ-bâⁿ ū sím-ê kè-ta̍t?
answer: Tī 'Sàng chè-chok sî ê chōng-thài' ê muî-chi̍t hāng lóng ū kāng-ê kè-ta̍t 'Chāi kiàn-siat tiong' choán-pêng ê siàu-phiⁿ.

question: Tī 4 go̍eh ê chá-sì-ê chiu-ji̍t, tē 1 kàu tē 4 chi̍p lóng chhut-lâi. Chún-tēng che chi̍p thiah-khui liáu chit ê chiu-ji̍t chi̍t chi̍p ê sî-kan ê tē-it chi̍p, koh hō͘ lâng chai-iáⁿ i ê chhut-lâi sî-kan só͘ chha-ì ê só͘-chāi.
answer: "Kiàn-siat Se-pa-nî siāng tōa ê kiô" chit chi̍p sī tē-it chi̍p thiah-khui chit ê sî-kan tōa-chè. Kū-liáu tē 1 kàu tē 4 chi̍p ê sî-kan liáu-liáu sī 7 kang chi̍t pái, chit chi̍p sī tī 2011 nî 6 go̍eh 18 ji̍t chhut-lâi, jî-chhiáⁿ chiap chi̍t chi̍p tī 2011 nî 4 go̍eh 29 ji̍t, mā sī 50 kang āu, koh sī chiu-la̍k ê ji̍t-cháu, put-kò sī sì-ji̍t ê ji̍t.

question: Koh kok-ka ū chi̍t ê chiàⁿ 2011 nî 6 goe̍h ê khai-bō͘? (Which country had a project air in June 2011?)
